Easy Garden Salad

10 min
$6.5
150 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 2

Dietary Tags:

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Description

A refreshing mix of fresh vegetables, perfect for a light meal or side dish!

Ingredients

  • lettuce: 1 head (or 1 bag pre-washed)
  • cherry tomatoes: 1 cup
  • cucumber: 1
  • carrot: 1
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • balsamic vinegar: 1 tablespoon
  • salt: to taste
  • pepper: to taste
